listitem.para:
Automatically edit fields: &SYS_PRODUCT_NAME; 
                    includes fields that are automatically set : "Artifact ID", "Last Update Date", "Submitted By" and "Submitted On".
                    The users can't edit that fields.

section.para:
At the end of the Sprint (after two to four weeks), the team meets
      for the new Sprint Meeting. User stories selected in the past Sprint are updated, 
      and new stories are selected for the next Sprint.

